#: ../../F/finger-trouble.rst:5
msgid "finger trouble"
msgstr "finger trouble"

#: ../../F/finger-trouble.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../F/finger-trouble.rst:9
msgid ""
"Mistyping, typos, or generalized keyboard incompetence (this is surprisingly"
" common among hackers, given the amount of time they spend at keyboards). "
"\"I keep putting colons at the end of statements instead of semicolons\", "
"\"Finger trouble again, eh? \"."
msgstr ""
"打ち間違い、タイポ、あるいは全般的なキーボードの不器用さ(これはハッカーがキーボードに費やす時間を考えると、意外なほどよくある)。「文の終わりにセミコロンの代わりにコロンを置き続けてしまうんだ」「またfinger"
" troubleかい?」。"
